{"tid":617721,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城隊巴被攻擊 高普致歉","createTime":"2018-04-05T07:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T14:48:06.000Z","uid":4661,"like":62,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b42505148576292fe6e45d9c3bc0b11d4b94f2d4","tid":617721,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/8/378/20953324378/20960865801_600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F8%2F378%2F20953324378%2F20960865801_600x400.jpg&h=3b87a34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=9oYtqNZ0kmcTOiMphptbCcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4d545705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼城在周三歐聯作客利物浦，在隊巴駛進球場前，被利迷投擲煙花及啤酒樽。<br />\n<br />\n歐聯8強首回合，曼城先作客利物浦，大軍乘坐隊巴去到晏菲路球場前，已有一大群紅軍球迷「恭候」，更有人向隊巴投擲煙花、啤酒樽、汽水罐，希望擾亂一眾藍月球員，先來個下馬威。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦官方及領隊高普（Jurgen Klopp）皆在比賽開始之前向曼城道歉。高普說：「我真的不明白他們為甚麼要這樣做。我們用盡一切方法去防止這些事件發生。我代表利物浦作出道歉。」<br />\n<br />\n至於曼城主帥哥迪奧拿亦大方回應：「多謝高普的道歉。我們沒有預到情況會是這樣，我知道這不是利物浦，生事的4至10人絕對不代表這家球會的歷史。」"},{"pid":"b304eb8c7281a466b1cb5f89ef9d936c81d2c83a","tid":617721,"uid":89134,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"原來痢狗出茅招 影響人作賽"},{"pid":"8ae2ad5b2a0a1f5bd8b15ac25ba78ccf1a09bfab","tid":617721,"uid":53672,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母道歉當無野?要重賽啦"},{"pid":"2ef30ec1e072c3f6d75fd1d562dc3afee8adda2a","tid":617721,"uid":11254,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"唔知以為曼城利物浦世仇<br />\n由頭HER到尾 仲搞鳩人隊巴"},{"pid":"1e16d5bbd96b89af6e5420e8cdbff23540b3df91","tid":61772